│ signed range and exceeds unsigned maximum for some cases; adding nuw/nsw is   │
│ incorrect. The LVI range used at the trunc use point appears overly           │
│ optimistic or not globally valid, leading CVP to mark trunc as nuw/nsw even   │
│ though values outside the i8 range are possible. With trunc, nuw/nsw          │
