│ 1215-1240\n- Change: Disable or tighten the deduction of nuw/nsw flags on     │
│ trunc. The safest immediate fix is to stop setting these flags entirely in    │
│ CVP to avoid introducing poison semantics erroneously. Specifically, modify   │
│ processTrunc to simply return false (i.e., perform no changes), or guard      │
