│ not fit the destination type.\n    return false;\n  }\n\nAlternatively, if we │
│ prefer to keep the function shape and stats but avoid mutations:\n  - Keep    │
│ the function but remove the logic that calls TI->setHasNoUnsignedWrap and     │
│ TI->setHasNoSignedWrap; just compute Range and return false.\n\nRationale:    │
